prodNameE: Binax NOW Legionella Urinary Antigen Test
ingredientsDesc:
Test Devices: A membrone coated with robbit antibody specific for Legionella pneumophila serogroup 1 antigen and with goat anti-rabbit IgG is combined with rabbit anti-Legionella pneumophila serogroup 1 antigen conjugate in a hinged test device.
Reagent A - Citrate / Phosphate with Tween 20 and Azide.
Swabs - Designed for use in the Binax NOW Legionella Urinary Antigen Test.
Positive Control Swab - Heat inactivated L. pneumophila dried onto swab.
Negative Control Swab - L. pneumophila negative swab.
